text.section:
The Liquor Control Board may issue a Class CCFA license to a continuing care facility for the aged that:
Provides continuing care as defined in § 10-401 of the Human Services Article;
Is licensed as a related institution under Title 19, Subtitle 3 of the Health - General Article;
Is certified by the Department of Aging;
Is exempt from federal income tax under § 501(c)(3) of the Internal Revenue Code; and
Is located in Harford County.
